folder: Franklin Avenue & Myrtle Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
157-173 Franklin Ave., east side, between Myrtle Ave., and Willoughby street. Also seen is the Franklin Ave. Italian Presbyterian Church, at no. 161-171 Franklin Ave.

July 22, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, an earlier view.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
